name: Cyrce's Circlet
description: Sea dogs and tale spinners tell stories of a mythical siren that could lure even the stubbornest sailors to a watery grave.

spells.description:
Use: Open the pouch and draw Nx's shadow blade to quickly strike at enemies in front of you, inflicting 174,489 Shadow damage to all enemies hit.

You may use the pouch up to two additional times within 20 sec before it seals itself to magically recharge its contents. (2 Min Cooldown)
Equip: Your attacks have a chance to mark their targets as Dead Ahead. Attacking the marked target grants 956 Critical Strike for 10 sec, stacking up to 5 times.
Equip: Your gear cools with Woven Duskthread and gains 756 Versatility when over 80% health.

Equip: Gain Ascendance every 8 seconds spent in combat.

Ascendance grants 89 of a random secondary stat for 15 sec, stacking up to 10 times.

This is a Nerubian embellishment.
